name: Vivian O'Sullivan
profile_summary: This 35-year-old woman is a Public Relations Specialist in the Media & Communication industry. Standing at a height of 5'7", she is a graduate from Dublin City University in her hometown of Dublin, Ireland but is currently dating in Los Angeles, California. She has a deeply held value for kindness, family and hard work. She can communicate in both English and Gaelic and enjoys reading, cooking, and hiking. Although she is a practicing Catholic and holds liberal political views, she is looking for a long term monogamous relationship. She identifies as straight, has no children but hopes to start a family in the future. As a physically active individual, she sometimes drinks, but never smokes or uses marijuana or drugs. She is a proud pet parent to her dog and is an ENFJ Virgo.
preferences_summary: The user is seeking a man who is aged between 30 to 40 years, stands anywhere from 5'6'' to 6'2'' in height and has no children but wants them in the future. The ideal match would identify as straight and be keen on long-term dating leading to monogamy. The user prefers her partner to be a non-smoker, not use marijuana or drugs, but someone who enjoys a drink and leads an active lifestyle. The ideal match would be of Black African Descent, Hispanic/Latino, or be White Caucasian. The user appreciates men of liberal or moderate political views, who work in Media & Communication, Technology, or Marketing sectors. Such a man should be able to communicate in English and share the user's values of kindness, hard work, and family. Reading, cooking, and hiking are interests that the user wishes to share with her partner. Additionally, the potential match should have achieved at least an undergraduate level of education.
